OL,3,CBid to overturn loyalist 'show of
OL,4,Cstrength' conviction
OL,6,FA man jailed for taking part in a so-
OL,7,Fcalled loyalist show of strength in
OL,8,Feast Belfast has launched a legal bid
OL,9,Fto overturn his conviction.
OL,11,FDerek George Lammey, 60, is serving an
OL,12,F18-month sentence for an intimidation
OL,13,Foffence connected to a gathering of up
OL,14,Fto 40 masked men in February 2021.
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland's most senior judge,
OL,17,FLady Chief Justice Dame Siobhan
OL,18,FKeegan, has agreed to hear his appeal
OL,19,Fagainst the guilty verdict early next
OL,20,Fyear.
