OL,3,CBid to overturn loyalist 'show of
OL,4,Cstrength' conviction
OL,6,FLammey, of Spring Place in the city,
OL,7,Fwas convicted following a non-jury
OL,8,Ftrial at Belfast Crown Court.
OL,10,FThe charge related to a group of men
OL,11,Fwho gathered in the Pitt Park area and
OL,12,Fwalked to a nearby community centre.
OL,14,FA number of women and children were
OL,15,Fsaid to have taken shelter inside the
OL,16,Fbuilding, including the wife and
OL,17,Fdaughter of murdered east Belfast man
OL,18,FIan Ogle.
