OL,3,CBid to overturn loyalist 'show of
OL,4,Cstrength' conviction
OL,6,FMr Ogle was beaten and stabbed to
OL,7,Fdeath near his home at Cluan Place
OL,8,Fback in January 2019.
OL,10,FAt his trial Lammey was acquitted on
OL,11,Fseparate charges of unlawful assembly
OL,12,Fand affray over the Pitt Park incident.
OL,14,FBut the judge found him guilty of
OL,15,Fintimidation through taking part in
OL,16,Fwhat was described as a show of
OL,17,Fstrength by an unspecified loyalist
OL,18,Forganisation.
