OL,3,CBid to overturn loyalist 'show of
OL,4,Cstrength' conviction
OL,6,FCo-accused Stephen Matthews, 62, with
OL,7,Fan address at Pansy Street in Belfast,
OL,8,Fwas cleared on all charges of being
OL,9,Fpart of the masked group.
OL,11,FLammey's lawyers have now lodged up to
OL,12,Fseven grounds of appeal against his
OL,13,Fconviction.
OL,15,FA further challenge to the sentence
OL,16,Fimposed on him centres on a dispute
OL,17,Fabout any alleged terrorist connection
OL,18,Fto the events at Pitt Park.
